      <h2 class="case-study__company">Bright Funds</h4>
      <h1 class="case-study__title">Redesigning a key feature to help people give more effectively</h3>
      <div class="case-study__role">Lead Designer / Team of 3</div>
      <img src="../images/cs-foundation-fund/case-study_foundation-funds.jpg" class="case-study-preview__img" alt="Foundation Fund Product Design Case Study">
